### ===================================================================
### CREATE YOUR OWN (Via API)
### ===================================================================

### Create a Custom Search Tool
POST {{baseUrl}}/tools/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "my_news_search",
  "name": "My News Search",
  "type": "websearch",
  "config": {
    "engine": "duckduckgo",
    "max_results": 8,
    "region": "us-en",
    "safesearch": "moderate",
    "timelimit": "d"
  },
  "version": "v1"
}

### Create an Agent Using Your Tool
POST {{baseUrl}}/agents/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "my_news_agent",
  "name": "My News Agent",
  "type": "react",
  "llm_config": {
    "provider": "groq",
    "model": "llama-3.1-70b-versatile",
    "temperature": 0.3
  },
  "tools": ["my_news_search"],
  "version": "v1"
}

### Create a Workflow Using Your Agent
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "my_news_workflow",
  "name": "My News Workflow",
  "type": "sequence",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "search_news",
      "agent_ref": "my_news_agent",
      "task": "Find news about ${parameters.topic}"
    }
  ],
  "version": "v1"
}

### Execute Your Custom Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/my_news_workflow/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parameters": {
    "topic": "renewable energy"
  }
}

